item.content:encoded:
TRAINING SESSIONS

In a friendly and warm atmosphere, discover your gym and its different spaces

Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.
  • Cardio and bodybuilding areas.
  • A space for group lessons.
  • State-certified coaches.
  • Quality Equipment.
Join us today Cardio Training

Let's go!

Cardio class

Challenge your self everyday

Explore Our Classes

FAQ

Questions

FAQ

Frequently asked questions from customers

What are the gym's opening hours?

We are open from 6am to 10pm every day of the week, including weekends.

What is the cancellation policy?
If you need to cancel your membership, please notify us at least 30 days prior to the expiration date of your contract.
What are the rates for a monthly membership?
Our monthly membership rates start at $50 per month. We also offer special rates for students, seniors and groups.
Do you offer group classes?
Yes, we offer a variety of group classes including yoga, cardio, weight training and dance. You can check our online calendar to see class schedules.
Do you provide towels and toiletries?
Yes, we provide towels and toiletries for your convenience. Please note that towels must be returned at the end of each workout.
Can I bring a guest with me?

Yes, you may bring a guest with you for an additional fee. Please contact the front desk for details.

Do you offer personal training sessions?
Yes, we offer personal training sessions with our professional instructors. Please contact the front desk for more details and to schedule your personal training session.

item.content:encoded:
Coach

In a friendly and warm atmosphere, discover your gym and its different spaces

Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.
  • Cardio and bodybuilding areas.
  • A space for group lessons.
  • State-certified coaches.
  • Quality Equipment.
Join us today Cardio Training

Let's go!

John doe class

Challenge your self everyday

Explore Our Classes

FAQ

Questions

FAQ

Frequently asked questions from customers

What are the gym's opening hours?

We are open from 6am to 10pm every day of the week, including weekends.

What is the cancellation policy?
If you need to cancel your membership, please notify us at least 30 days prior to the expiration date of your contract.
What are the rates for a monthly membership?
Our monthly membership rates start at $50 per month. We also offer special rates for students, seniors and groups.
Do you offer group classes?
Yes, we offer a variety of group classes including yoga, cardio, weight training and dance. You can check our online calendar to see class schedules.
Do you provide towels and toiletries?
Yes, we provide towels and toiletries for your convenience. Please note that towels must be returned at the end of each workout.
Can I bring a guest with me?

Yes, you may bring a guest with you for an additional fee. Please contact the front desk for details.

Do you offer personal training sessions?
Yes, we offer personal training sessions with our professional instructors. Please contact the front desk for more details and to schedule your personal training session.

item.title: About US
item.dc:creator: ananass
item.content:encoded:
Who we are

Welcome to High Point

At High Point, we're passionate about climbing. Our facility is more than just a gym – it's a community of climbers united by their love for the sport. Expertise
  • Discover

Our Mission

Scaling New Heights Safely

Our mission is to provide a safe, supportive, and inspiring environment where climbers of all levels can challenge themselves and grow.
  • State-of-the-art climbing walls
  • Certified instructors
  • Innovative training programs
  • Social events and competitions
  • Outdoor excursions
Join us today

TRAIN WITH US

Join Us Today!

Ready to take your climbing to new heights? Sign up now and become part of the High Point community! Witness
  • Climbers

item.title: Classes
item.dc:creator: ananass
item.content:encoded:
What we do

Climbing Basics

Learn the fundamentals of climbing in this introductory class. Our experienced instructors will teach you basic techniques, safety procedures, and proper equipment usage. Perfect for beginners! Specialized
  • Discover

Climbing 101

Scaling New Heights Safely

Ready to take your climbing skills to the next level? Join our Climbing 101 class and learn advanced techniques, such as lead climbing, belaying, and route reading. Suitable for intermediate climbers. Join us today Specialized
  • Discover

Workshops

Bouldering Techniques

Master the art of bouldering in this specialized workshop. Improve your strength, agility, and problem-solving skills as you tackle challenging boulder problems with guidance from our expert coaches. Join us today Fitness
  • Climber's

Conditioning

Climber's Conditioning

Improve your climbing performance and prevent injuries with our Climber's Conditioning class. Focus on strength, flexibility, and core stability to become a stronger and more resilient climber. Join us today

Classes

Ready to Ascend?

Discover our site and its various areas

Who we are

Welcome to High Point

At High Point, we're passionate about climbing. Our facility is more than just a gym – it's a community of climbers united by their love for the sport.

Club near you

Welcome to High Point

At High Point, we're passionate about climbing. Our facility is more than just a gym – it's a community of climbers united by their love for the sport.

item.dc:creator: ananass
item.content:encoded:
Who we are

Scaling New Heights Safely

Title post 1

Scaling New Heights Safely

to High Point Climbing Gym, where adventure awaits around every corner. Whether you're a seasoned climber or just starting out, our state-of-the-art facility offers something for everyone. With over 50 climbing routes, from beginner-friendly walls to challenging overhangs, there's always a new challenge to conquer. Our experienced instructors are here to guide you every step of the way, helping you improve your technique and reach new heights. Join us for a day of climbing, meet fellow climbers, and discover the thrill of scaling the walls at High Point Climbing Gym.

item.content:encoded:
Who we are

Scaling New Heights Safely

Title post 1

Scaling New Heights Safely

to High Point Climbing Gym, where adventure awaits around every corner. Whether you're a seasoned climber or just starting out, our state-of-the-art facility offers something for everyone. With over 50 climbing routes, from beginner-friendly walls to challenging overhangs, there's always a new challenge to conquer. Our experienced instructors are here to guide you every step of the way, helping you improve your technique and reach new heights. Join us for a day of climbing, meet fellow climbers, and discover the thrill of scaling the walls at High Point Climbing Gym.

Who we are

Welcome to High Point

At High Point, we're passionate about climbing. Our facility is more than just a gym – it's a community of climbers united by their love for the sport. Expertise
  • Discover

Our Mission

Scaling New Heights Safely

Our mission is to provide a safe, supportive, and inspiring environment where climbers of all levels can challenge themselves and grow.
  • State-of-the-art climbing walls
  • Certified instructors
  • Innovative training programs
  • Social events and competitions
  • Outdoor excursions
Join us today

TRAIN WITH US

Join Us Today!

Ready to take your climbing to new heights? Sign up now and become part of the High Point community! Witness
  • Climbers

Who we are

Scaling New Heights Safely

Title post 1

Scaling New Heights Safely

to High Point Climbing Gym, where adventure awaits around every corner. Whether you're a seasoned climber or just starting out, our state-of-the-art facility offers something for everyone. With over 50 climbing routes, from beginner-friendly walls to challenging overhangs, there's always a new challenge to conquer. Our experienced instructors are here to guide you every step of the way, helping you improve your technique and reach new heights. Join us for a day of climbing, meet fellow climbers, and discover the thrill of scaling the walls at High Point Climbing Gym.

Who we are

Scaling New Heights Safely

Title post 1

Scaling New Heights Safely

to High Point Climbing Gym, where adventure awaits around every corner. Whether you're a seasoned climber or just starting out, our state-of-the-art facility offers something for everyone. With over 50 climbing routes, from beginner-friendly walls to challenging overhangs, there's always a new challenge to conquer. Our experienced instructors are here to guide you every step of the way, helping you improve your technique and reach new heights. Join us for a day of climbing, meet fellow climbers, and discover the thrill of scaling the walls at High Point Climbing Gym.
